INSERT INTO notes VALUES('01KMPHEM2YAYTC5NXBA575S901','01KMKRVYF2FN68D9N3C8BEGAHS','01KMKRVYF3YW28Q3P5EPSYC9M1','aidan',NULL,'Critical architecture decision: Qoopia evolves from passive CRM to active observer + agent memory system. Askhat rejected AGENTS.md rules and cron jobs as kostyl (crutch). Approved: Activity-First MCP with note/recall/brief tools, graceful degradation (Haiku+Voyage when available, keyword+FTS5 fallback), qoopia-observer hook for lossless-claw integration. Estimated ~$2/month cost.','01KMKRVYF3S266JM3WTR3J6T2H','mcp',NULL,'[{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9NGTFR6366R01V945","name":"Qoopia ребрендинг + домены","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMP64BDMA33RQ1ZK13WP5SWC","name":"Qoopia V2 LIVE + MCP connector + 25 tools","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMPERGDX16283EMH5VEHBCTK","name":"Qoopia Memory Layer: note / recall / brief deployed","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9KDDS81EFEENGFYN8","name":"Agents HQ Telegram forum created","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9P0GE79D31Q8M5P6S","name":"Правило 24 AGENTS.md: /code-review перед деплоем скриптов","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMP642THGR5H0DC5M39V6AG0","name":"Правило 25 AGENTS.md: WhatsApp config protection","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8JGV232BC7PKWPSFW","name":"Alan/Aizek memory/ — ждём первых записей","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9KVKKMG7PRSHG9859","name":"MCP Filesystem Server deployed","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8PV3N822ZSWZ1MNK5","name":"Zombie MCP processes — cron cleanup","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMPB57M9EKGSZPHBS6GZZQ8N","name":"Activity-First MCP: report_activity + smart responses + /observe","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMP64R2YQNPFPC6AHYYPT5W9","name":"Gmail hook fix (channel telegram→last)","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9RSBSQT9T3B5KW190","name":"Lossless-Claw v0.4.0 deplo