INSERT INTO notes VALUES('01KMPHEN80EC4BTXYYS1FXXMQR','01KMKRVYF2FN68D9N3C8BEGAHS','01KMKRVYF3YW28Q3P5EPSYC9M1','aidan',NULL,'Added rule ИССЛЕДОВАНИЕ != ЗАДАЧА to AGENTS.md. Research and discussions do NOT auto-create tasks in Qoopia. Tasks only on explicit Askhat command. Triggered by Fish Audio, HeyGen, NJ Sonic discussions creating phantom tasks.','01KMKRVYF3S266JM3WTR3J6T2H','mcp',NULL,'[{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9KDDS81EFEENGFYN8","name":"Agents HQ Telegram forum created","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9P0GE79D31Q8M5P6S","name":"Правило 24 AGENTS.md: /code-review перед деплоем скриптов","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMP642THGR5H0DC5M39V6AG0","name":"Правило 25 AGENTS.md: WhatsApp config protection","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9NGTFR6366R01V945","name":"Qoopia ребрендинг + домены","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMP64BDMA33RQ1ZK13WP5SWC","name":"Qoopia V2 LIVE + MCP connector + 25 tools","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMPERGDX16283EMH5VEHBCTK","name":"Qoopia Memory Layer: note / recall / brief deployed","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF95ZHX1N18XP8JKZ66","name":"Fish Audio — оценка и тестирование","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF93XA2W74PG2A51Y5W","name":"HeyGen Digital Twin — аватар Асхата","confidence":"medium"}]','[]','2026-03-27T02:19:57Z');
INSERT INTO notes VALUES('01KMPJ0NG8T63CBJFR9ZEQAJBP','01KMKRVYF2FN68D9N3C8BEGAHS','01KMKRVYF3YW28Q3P5EPSYC9M1','claude',NULL,'INSIGHT: Сравнение мнений Claude и Aidan по стратегии Qoopia. Совпадения (90%): GitHub first, MIT лицензия, патент не приоритет, скорость > защита, dashboard = пульс а не таблица. Различия: Aidan предлагает Alert/Pulse/Board три слоя — я предлагал похожее но без формализации слоёв. Aidan даёт конкретный traction (10 stars неделя 1, 50 stars месяц 1) — я не давал цифр. Aidan говорит "Dashboard нужно делать красиво, вау" — согласен, но добавляю: CLI/MCP experience первый, dashboard второй. Общий вывод обоих: GitHub launch до 28 марта, README = витрина, "Your AI agents forget everything. Qoopia fixes that."','01KMKRVYF3S266JM3WTR3J6T2H','mcp',X'','[{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF932MHQ6WNVMN8844X","name":"Zoe: Сауле — openclaw configure --section model (Claude Max OAuth)","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMP64K3A4BE134Y8YQWES6BB","name":"Claude Max переподписка Apple→Web ($200/мес)","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMPB4ZCCZ7HGNBMX17JPBJAK","name":"Claude Code: Opus по умолчанию + таймаут 20 мин","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF61MEDTQDP44KXJJN9","name":"Миграция КЗ-направления с Aidan на Aizek","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9NGTFR6366R01V945","name":"Qoopia ребрендинг + домены","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMP64BDMA33RQ1ZK13WP5SWC","name":"Qoopia V2 LIVE + MCP connector + 25 tools","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMPERGDX16283EMH5VEHBCTK","name":"Qoopia Memory Layer: note / recall / brief deployed","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9H32B1T540QZDXWJ7","name":"Stepper: GitHub public launch (Фаза 1)","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8CCYGC50PKX7SR8Q2","name":"GitHub Sync настроен","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8B1KJV7JV1HZ4MD4E","name":"Qoopia: GitHub public launch (Phase 1)","confidence