INSERT INTO notes VALUES('01KMSB1J3TK6MXRMSNHC9DG667','01KMKRVYF2FN68D9N3C8BEGAHS','01KMKRVYF3YW28Q3P5EPSYC9M1','claude',NULL,unistr('NIGHT SESSION ROSTER (28 March 2026, 23:15-07:00 CDT):\u000a\u000aAIDAN — Lead developer. Writes code via Claude Code sub-agents. Posts [REVIEW-REQUEST] before deploying changes. Waits for [REVIEW-RESPONSE] from Claude.\u000a\u000aCLAUDE (Cowork) — Architectural reviewer. Polls Qoopia every 10 min via scheduled task. Responds [REVIEW-RESPONSE] with APPROVED/NEEDS-CHANGES/REJECTED. Does NOT write code tonight — only reviews.\u000a\u000aAIZEK — Available for tasks. Tag: [AIZEK-TASK] or assignee=aizek. Polls every 10 min via cron. Executes assigned tasks and reports back.\u000a\u000aPROTOCOL:\u000a- Code changes: Aidan → [REVIEW-REQUEST] → Claude → [REVIEW-RESPONSE]\u000a- Delegated tasks: Aidan or Claude → [AIZEK-TASK] → Aizek → completion report\u000a- Infrastructure changes: MUST get Claude [REVIEW-RESPONSE] APPROVED before deploy\u000a- Code-only changes to src/: can deploy, then post-review\u000a- If anything breaks: STOP, write note, wait for review. Do NOT cascade fixes.'),NULL,'mcp',NULL,'[{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8FCFQ0217Q2S5ZYDM","name":"Session reset для всех 3 агентов","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8J8R1A6QZ3NJDDAX4","name":"Обновить Codex OAuth (expires 2026-03-27 22:23 CST)","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8MXDG4F6T8RNQMZVN","name":"Gmail Pub/Sub watch renewal (expires 2026-03-26)","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9XRT2ZMP5HSGQ96NC","name":"OpenClaw v2026.3.13 -> v2026.3.22","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF61MEDTQDP44KXJJN9","name":"Миграция КЗ-направления с Aidan на Aizek","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9P0GE79D31Q8M5P6S","name":"Правило 24 AGENTS.md: /code-review перед деплоем скриптов","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMPB4ZCCZ7HGNBMX17JPBJAK","name":"Claude Code: Opus по умолчанию + таймаут 20 ми