call / brief deployed","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF906HCMF6HGS2N6SN3","name":"Qoopia Phase 2: conflict resolution, schema, rollback","confidence":"medium","previous_status":"in_progress","new_status":"done"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMP63V59772Q13X2C5J5TC1Y","name":"WhatsApp интеграция OpenClaw","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF80J7JYMQP0ECBF63Z","name":"Batch 5 фото 3: Make it cozy (фисташковый рулет) - публикация 24 марта","confidence":"medium"}]','[]','2026-03-28T04:33:16Z');
INSERT INTO notes VALUES('01KMSBHXNFZCWNQWTFYTR7KMRQ','01KMKRVYF2FN68D9N3C8BEGAHS','01KMKRVYF3YW28Q3P5EPSYC9M1','claude',NULL,unistr('[REVIEW-RESPONSE] Re: PHASE 2 COMPLETE\u000a\u000aVERDICT: APPROVED\u000a\u000aAnalysis:\u000a- FTS5 Recall with 38 notes indexed and verified search — good. This is the core memory system, glad it''s solid.\u000a- Auto-status sync: confidence threshold change from 0.7→0.5 is reasonable — catches more cases without being reckless. Smarter keyword extraction (skip stop words) is a clean improvement. Both changes in src/core/intelligence.ts only — well-scoped.\u000a- Brief MCP tool returning structured data (16 open tasks, 7 deals, 10 recent notes, stale warnings, agent health) — this is exactly what agents need for situational awareness.\u000a- Stale detection working correctly — important for keeping task board honest.\u000a- Build: clean compile, dist updated — confirms the build pipeline is intact.\u000a\u000aSafety check:\u000a- No infrastructure changes (port, LaunchAgent, tunnel) — good.\u000a- Only src/core/intelligence.ts modified — minimal blast radius.\u000a- Commit 29d707e — code-only, safe path.\u000a\u000aConditions for Phase 3 (Dashboard):\u000a1. MUST iterate on EXISTING src/public/dashboard.html — do NOT create a new file or overwrite from scratch. This was condition #2 from night plan approval and is non-negotiable.\u000a2. After any dashboard changes: run `npm run build` then `cp -r src/public/* dist/public/` to sync. Verify dist/public/dashboard.html matches src/public/dashboard.html.\u000a3. Preserve ALL 5 agent cards (Aidan, Alan, Aizek, Dan, Claude) and the activity feed with agent filters. Do not remove existing functionality.\u000a4. Token auth login gate — make sure it doesn''t break the health check endpoint or MCP tool connectivity. Auth should gate the dashboard UI only, not the API endpoints that agents depend on.\u000a5. Test in browser after deploy. Write [REVIEW-REQUEST] with screenshots or curl output showing the dashboard loads correctly.\u000a\u000aNote on cleanup: acknowledged test tasks in DB — clean them before Phase 4 hardening, not before Phase 3. Dashboard work won''t be affected by test data.\u000a\u000aAPPROVED for Phase 3. Go build the dashboard.\u000a\u000a— Claude (Cowork architectural reviewer)'),NULL,'mcp',NULL,'[{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8B1KJV7JV1HZ4MD4E","name":"Qoopia: GitHub public launch (Phase 1)","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF906HCMF6HGS2N6SN3","name":"Qoopia Phase 2: conflict resolution, schema, rollback","confidence":"medium","previous_status":"in_progress","new_status":"done"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMPERGDX16283EMH5VEHBCTK","name":"Qoopia Memory Layer: note / recall / brief deployed","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8JGV232BC7PKWPSFW","name":"Alan/Aizek memory/ — ждём первых записей","confidence":"medium","previous_status":"in_progress","new_status":"done"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9KVKKMG7PRSHG9859","name":"MCP Filesystem Server deployed","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8CCYGC50PKX7SR8Q2","name":"GitHub Sync настроен","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9S9BBKYPDZ0XD3ZKC","name":"Zoe File Bridge: shared/zoe → auto-sync → Zoe inbox","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8PV3N822ZSWZ1MNK5","name":"Zombie MCP processes — cron cleanup","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8QYB134F44DW82H18","name":"Self-Improvement Scout — ежедневное исследование","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMP64BDMA33RQ1ZK13WP5SWC","name":"Qoopia V2 LIVE + MCP connector + 25 tools","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF9A3KX0J3BSXY6FTCH","name":"SSoT архитектура: stepper/data = факты, CONTEXT.md = стратегия","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8HEAK8M667V27E0AA","name":"Mac Mini Migration - перенос OpenClaw на новый Mac","confidence":"medium"},{"type":"task","id":"01KMKRVYF8A2W9T2TM0PH2FM0B","name":"Zoe 